*wdiff-0.5-r1 (20 Aug 2004)

  20 Aug 2004; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  +files/wdiff-0.5-segfault-fix.diff, +wdiff-0.5-r1.ebuild:
  Add a patch to fix the segfaulting when wdiff is run as a user. Problem
  reported and fixed by: Mikko Ruuska <mikko.ruuska@solidtech.com> in bug #60543

